87 reasons to vote Repost, link, embed, share and vote. From RISD.GD. More info First year BFA and MFA 3-year students in the RISD Graphic Design Department were asked to form and design a message to encourage their peers to vote in the 2018 U.S. midterm elections. User research led to concepts that led to ten designs that were evaluated in class. One graphic per student has been uploaded for a wider view. Assignment and website by Assoc. Professor John Caserta. See full assignment.
